chav1961.purelib.basic
This package contains a set of classes for the basic abilities of the library.

chav1961.purelib.enumerations
This package contains all popular enumerations used in the Pure Library

This package contains description of Pure Library internationalization classes.

This package contains description of locale-specific interfaces and annotations.
chav1961.purelib.json
This package contains useful classes to operate with JSON format.

This package contains interfaces and enumerations to work with JSON format.
chav1961.purelib.model
This package contains an API to use with models.
chav1961.purelib.model.interfaces  
chav1961.purelib.sql.interfaces

chav1961.purelib.streams
This package contains a set of classes and interfaces to support stream processing of the different sorts.
chav1961.purelib.streams.char2char
This package contains a set of output streams, that get character content and convert it to another appropriative character content.
